These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-1::.
7 different games are played: poker, scrabble, whist, snooker, domino, billiard, monopoly
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, turkish, dutch, mexican, russian, japanese, argentine
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, zombie, disaster, family, animation, satire, documentary
There 7 different types of food: pineapple, radish, grapefruit, spinach, raspberry, artichoke, lettuce
 1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 2. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
 3. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 4. the mexican is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
 5. the dutch is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
 6. the argentine is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 7. the turkish is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
 8. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
 9. the mexican is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
10. the person playing whist is somewhere between the dutch and the person eating pineapple##7
11. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the mexican##8
12. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
13. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
14. the person playing domino is not the person eating pineapple##6
15. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
16. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person watching action movies##8
17. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person eating grapefruit##8
18. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
19. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
20. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5
21. the person eating radish is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
22. the person eating pineapple is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
23. the person playing poker is the person watching animation movies##1
24. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
25. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the mexican##8
26. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
27. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
28. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the dutch##7
29. the turkish is on the right of the mexican##1
30. the person eating grapefruit is the person playing billiard##1
31. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the russian##3
32. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
33. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
34. the person playing domino is not the person eating artichoke##6
35. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
36. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
37. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
38. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the turkish##8
39. the argentine is not the person eating artichoke##6
40. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5        |       6       |       7       |
| Game      | domino   | scrabble     | monopoly    | poker      | billiard       | whist         | snooker |
| Nationality           | indonesian   | mexican | turkish | russian | japanese | argentine | dutch       |
